data.description: Bring your imagination! Beautifully located in the heart of the Edmonds Bowl. Short, walking distance to some of the best shopping and restaurants Edmonds has to offer. Inside, you’ll be greeted with a living/kitchen area. Brand new resurfaced hardwood floors, Down the hallway will have two bedrooms, including the primary with a full bathroom. Past the kitchen, you’ll find a sunroom and a second family room. Take the stairs to an upper loft for the third bedroom with access to your own private balcony/sundeck with peekaboo views of the sound. The backyard is fully fenced. Brand new WiFi garage doors and home is pre-inspected! This Prime Edmonds location is minutes to parks, the Ferry and the beaches.
